hours: Monday-Friday 8am to 5pm, other times by appointment
products: All types of Security hardware. From traditional knobsets and levers, to keyless entry or push button locks, to full length astragals and hinges, door closers and panic hardware, even weatherstripping.
services:
Complete Residential, Commercial, and Automotive Locksmithing Services.
 
Some of the Residential locksmithing services we offer include locks rekeyed or installed, replacing broken locks, repairing doors/jams after break-ins, and installing keyless entry locks.
 
Commercial services include rekeying locks, master key systems in apartment buildings, repairing/installing narrow stile glass/aluminum door hardware, adjusting and installing door closers, installing/repairing commercial keyless entry locks, installing/replacing electric strikes, repairing all kinds of panic hardware/crash bars, making keys for file cabinets, upgrading security on exterior doors with blocker plates, full length astragals, etc...

Automotive services include making keys for vehicles on site when all the keys have been lost, as well as programming extra keys for vehicles (OEM and aftermarket keys are fine). We can service almost all domestic and Japanese brands (European is trickier).
brands:
Residential brands include Weiser, Schlage, Kwikset, Don-Jo, and other offshore brands.
Commercial brands include Schlage, Corbin, Sargent, Kaba, Don-Jo, LCN, Adams Rite, Von Duprin, Dorex, LSDA, Scorpion, Halsco and dozens more.
